Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.45,0:22:21.86,note*,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz-65\fs48\c&H565454&\move(360,900,195,545,1,1892)}在慢慢顯現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 他聽到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.52,0:22:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,焰火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.28,0:23:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 能讓我陪著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.89,0:23:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在這樣我就已經很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個段子就用焰火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.78,0:23:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
